## Workflow Overview

We follow an 8-phase process:

1. **`/create-issue`** → Capture bugs/features to backlog
2. **`/explore`** → Deep analysis, ask questions, read code (no coding yet)
3. **`/create-plan`** → Generate markdown plan with progress tracking
4. **`/execute`** → Implement plan step-by-step
5. **`/review`** → Self-review code for issues
6. **`/peer-review`** → Cross-model validation
7. **`/document`** → Update docs and architecture notes
8. **`/learn`** → Teaching mode for understanding

See `CLAUDE.md` for detailed workflow documentation.

