## Model Preferences

When user manually switches models:

| Model | Use For | Why |
|-------|---------|-----|
| **Claude (via Claude Code extension)** | Planning, exploration, main development | Best at understanding context, asking questions |
| **GPT (via Codex extension)** | Gnarly bugs, complex debugging | Deep problem-solving |
| **Gemini (optional)** | UI/frontend design | Great visual results |
| **Cursor Composer** | Fast tasks | Blazing speed for simple work |

